dadfc8eb-0afa-49ac-8489-7478367022d8.a91b19fb-e239-43d5-bed5-8f8f33e2e783.prompt=Text to Replace\: dadfc8eb-0afa-49ac-8489-7478367022d8.aa42935f-949f-4d14-a470-182c9ae1474d.description=
Useful Op to keep a running results.
Takes a string input (resultText) and appends this to a global context key of "runningResults". As a result, the context key whose name is in the keyName input will be appended with the string from the input resultText.

Input Parameters\:
keyName - name of context key to append to
resultText - string input to append
delimiter - (leave blank for none) the delimiter to put between what is already in keyName before appending resultText

Responses\:
success - assigned the context variable

Returns\:
The the value of the context variable it appended to.

Context\:
runningResults

Scriptlet Example\:
currentResults \= scriptletContext.get("runningResults");

if (currentResults \=\= null) {
   currentResults \= resultText;
} else {
   currentResults +\= resultText;
}


scriptletContext.putGlobal("runningResults", currentResults);

dadfc8eb-0afa-49ac-8489-7478367022d8.db4a95ba-fc2c-4606-b905-cdcc25f96a57.prompt=Input String\: dadfc8eb-0afa-49ac-8489-7478367022d8.description=
Traverses and fetches a directory from a remote Secure FTP (SFTP) server to a local folder.

Inputs\:
host - IP address/host name of the SFTP server.
port - The port to connect to for the SFTP server.  Default is 22.
username - Remote username.
password - Password to authenticate with.  If using a priovate key file, this will be used as the passphrase for the file.
privateKey - Absolute path for private key file on the RAS for public/private key authentication.
remotePath - The remote directory to copy from.
localPath - The local directory to copy to.

Responses\:
success - Successfully retrieved the directory.
failure - Something went wrong.
